title: Catalonia's independence referendum, cartooned | The Economist
description:
Catalonia's independence referendum has ended with the Catalan president, Carles Puigdemont, stuck in a quagmire. Our cartoonist KAL talks through how he expressed those difficulties for his latest cartoon.
